            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>歐特克(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ADSK:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ADSK\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ADSK-US</a>)截至台北時間13日01:04股價下跌11.78美元，報220.81美元，跌幅5.06%，成交量1,471,774（股），盤中最高價235.19美元、最低價220.79美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-1.1%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-1.11%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-1.55%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-1.73%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>歐特克(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ADSK:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ADSK\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ADSK-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+0.07%</li> <li>近 1 月：-11.75%</li> <li>近 3 月：-19.31%</li> <li>近 6 月：-14.42%</li> <li>今年以來：-17.71%</li></ul></section></main>",
